In this section, we will describe the distribution of the different approaches to recommendations in our study in **TABLE 8** and **FIGURE 5**. Based on the analysis performed, we note that the strongest responses are hybrid approaches and approaches based on supervised and unsupervised learning. This comes back to the fact that hybrid approaches and approaches based on Machine Learning algorithms have shown their great performance, and that Machine Learning algorithms have become the most widely used at all levels and in all disciplines.

